        <comment xml:lang="en">Estimation. Data overtaken from Switzerland. Swiss data are calculated values based on the electricity transported in this voltage level (36796 GWh) and the total low voltage power line length in Switzerland (cables and aerial lines - 128646 km). Lifetime is assumed to be 40 years. See Itten&amp;Frischknecht 2012, Tab. 4.1 and Tab. 4.3.</comment>
